Package KI304.Stefaniv.Lab2

package KI304.Stefaniv.Lab2
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Footwear
    The `Footwear` class represents shoes with various properties such as brand, model, size, sole, laces, upper material, and lace status.
    FootwearDriver
    The `FootwearDriver` class and its main method serve as the entry point of the program and demonstrate the usage of the `Footwear` class to create footwear objects and interact with them.
    Laces
    The `Laces` class represents shoe laces with properties such as length and color.
    Sole
    The `Sole` class represents the sole of footwear with properties such as material and the presence of a tread.
    Upper
    The `Upper` class represents the upper material of footwear with the property - material.
